{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01P8gMpiavqDPATdZgzgU2oM","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: develop\n     3→description: \"새 기능 개발 워크플로우 가이드\"\n     4→---\n     5→\n     6→# Develop Skill\n     7→\n     8→## 설명\n     9→\n    10→새 기능을 개발할 때의 표준 워크플로우를 안내한다.\n    11→\n    12→## 개발 순서\n    13→\n    14→```\n    15→1. Entity 정의       → domain/.../entity/\n    16→2. Repository 작성   → domain/.../repository/\n    17→3. GraphQL Schema    → graphql/.../resources/graphql/\n    18→4. Proto 정의        → protobuf/.../proto/\n    19→5. Service 구현      → {module}/.../service/\n    20→6. gRPC Service      → {module}/.../controller/\n    21→7. GraphQL Service   → graphql/.../service/\n    22→8. GraphQL Controller → graphql/.../controller/\n    23→```\n    24→\n    25→## 계층별 역할\n    26→\n    27→| 계층 | 위치 | 역할 |\n    28→|------|------|------|\n    29→| GraphQL Controller | `graphql/controller/` | 요청 수신, 응답 조합, @PreAuthorize |\n    30→| GraphQL Service | `graphql/service/` | @GrpcClient로 gRPC 호출 |\n    31→| GrpcService | `{module}/controller/` | gRPC 요청 수신, Service 호출 |\n    32→| Service | `{module}/service/` | 비즈니스 로직, @Transactional |\n    33→| Repository | `domain/repository/` | DB 접근 (JPA/QueryDSL) |\n    34→\n    35→## 검증\n    36→\n    37→```bash\n    38→./gradlew :변경모듈:compileKotlin\n    39→./gradlew :변경모듈:test\n    40→```\n    41→\n    42→## 주의사항\n    43→\n    44→- GrpcService에 Repository 직접 주입 금지 (반드시 Service 경유)\n    45→- GraphQL Controller에서 Repository 접근 금지 (gRPC Service 경유)\n    46→- Proto 변경 시 `./gradlew :protobuf:build` 먼저 실행\n    47→- 상세 패턴은 `references/full-workflow.md` 참조\n    48→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01UKAeQuPwVAmYrHews1WSN5","session_id":"826096cf-4bcb-4174-96a5-8acb5127a76a","uuid":"e035ee3c-f2e2-40e9-86b1-e0cc4f031c49"}
